storm game engine
	ssys	- platform independence layer
			- platform detection
			- atomic data types
			- collections and iterators
			- file system
			- network transport layer
			- timer
			- threading
	core	- core systems
			- mathematics library
			- assertions
			- testing
			- memory management
			- logging
			- random number generator
			- profiling/statistics
			- configuration
	gear	- physics engine
			- hard body collisions
			- soft body collisions
			- kinematics
	rain	- rendering engine
			- textures
			- lighting
			- shadows
			- reflections
			- fonts



